polysoftk_lite — excerpt from PySoftK
=====================================

Upstream: https://github.com/alejandrosantanabonilla/pysoftk  
License: BSD 3-Clause (same as upstream PySoftK)  
Vendored git revision: da049f2437eff55fd2ed0e62c4de48aef8a1c51f  

This directory contains a minimal subset of PySoftK sufficient for
``Lp.linear_polymer()`` (RDKit assembly → PDB → Open Babel force-field
relaxation and rotor optimization). It is not the full PySoftK package;
do not treat it as a drop-in replacement outside this skill.

See the repository root LICENSE or upstream LICENSE for the full BSD-3-Clause text.
